comment._content: LoC has another copy of this picture, at www.loc.gov/pictures/item/2009631742/ with summary: Print shows Archduke Friedrich, Duke of Teschen, and Baron Conrad von Hötzendorf standing in front of a large group of military officers at the general headquarters of the Austro-Hungarian Army. Archduke Friedrich of Austria, Duke of Teschen aka Habsburg, Frederick,--1856-1936. en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Archduke_Friedrich,_Duke_of_Teschen forum.alexanderpalace.org/index.php?topic=6463.0 has some pictures of him Conrad von Hötzendorf, Franz,--Graf,--1852-1925. en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Count_Franz_Conrad_von_H%C3%B6tzendorf
